<h2>🚚 Fleet Booking Request Received</h2>

<p>Hello {{name}},</p>

<p>
  Thank you for your request. We’ve received your fleet booking details and our team will reach out to you shortly to confirm availability, logistics, and final pricing.
</p>

<hr/>

<h3>📍 Your Request Summary</h3>

<p><strong>Pickup:</strong> {{pickup}}</p>
<p><strong>Destination:</strong> {{destination}}</p>
<p><strong>Date:</strong> {{date}}</p>
<p><strong>Time:</strong> {{time}}</p>
<p><strong>Passengers:</strong> {{passengerCount}}</p>

{{#if cargoDescription}}
  <p><strong>Cargo:</strong> {{cargoDescription}}</p>
{{/if}}

{{#if specialRequests}}
  <p><strong>Special Requests:</strong></p>
  <p>{{specialRequests}}</p>
{{/if}}

<hr/>

<p>
  📧 We will contact you via <strong>{{email}}</strong><br/>
  📞 Or call you on <strong>{{phone}}</strong>
</p>

<p style="margin-top: 10px; font-size: 13px; color: #666;">
  *Final pricing may vary based on distance, load requirements, and current market conditions.
</p>

<p style="margin-top: 20px;">
  — Novo Car Fleet Team
</p>